      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WILD BEAU (5) is a course and distance specialist who was safely held in Adelaide two back then back on his favourite track absolutely bolted in last time. Looks the one to beat again. ARIZONA ACTIVIST (3) showed good early dash last start and held on well to finish a head back in second over 1200m at this track. Was a strong winner the start prior. Going well for the new yard and will take catching again. CINQUE TORRI (1) finished fourth over 1200m at Alice Springs at his most recent appearance on May 2. Has two wins and two minors from four starts this circuit. Should do much better. FIELD OF FLUTES (2) scored last start at this track to make it two wins from two starts this campaign. In sparkling form and will take catching again. CONVINCEBILITY (7) resumes. Goes well fresh and has placed 3/3 course and distance and is worth including.",
